        <abstract>
            <p>Will do his best to get observations on expression among the Chinese.</p>
            <p>Reports observations on hedgehogs collecting fruit with their spines.</p>
            <p>Discusses the domestic pig of Formosa, its wild ancestors, and its capacity to breed with other races.</p>
        </abstract>
